Class Cons

java.lang.Object
FunList
Cons
public class Cons extends FunList
Represents a non-empty functional list (cons cell). This class holds a value and a reference to the tail of the list. It is used to construct functional lists by linking values.
Since:
JDK1.4
Author:
Mykhailo Rytsariev
